<h2>Chapter 1: The 8 Agency Pricing Models</h2>
<p>Before deciding what to charge, you need to decide how to charge. The pricing model you choose shapes every contract, every deliverable, and every client conversation that follows.</p>
<p>According to a <a href="https://seranking.com/blog/seo-pricing/">2025 agency pricing survey by SE Ranking</a>, 78.2% of SEOs charge monthly retainers, 34.8% bill by the hour, and 48.9% charge project-based fees. A smaller 9% use performance-based pricing. Most agencies blend 2 or 3 models depending on the client type and scope.</p>
<p>Here is how all 8 models compare:</p>
