<h2>Chapter 2: Monthly Retainer Pricing. The Agency Standard</h2>
<p>Monthly retainers are the backbone of most agencies. They create predictable revenue, enable long-term planning, and align agency incentives with client growth.</p>
<p>Retainers work because most agency services are not one-time projects. SEO requires ongoing technical maintenance, content creation, link building, and continuous adaptation to algorithm changes. Social media management requires daily attention. Content marketing requires consistent publishing. A retainer model funds that work over the 6–12 months it takes to see meaningful results.</p>
<h3>What Retainer Pricing Looks Like in 2026</h3>
